                "x": -710,
                "y": -160
            },
            "markdown": "## 🔁 Workflow Description\n\nAutomatically deliver a **detailed ROI calculation** and route follow-up actions based on the contact’s lifecycle stage and engagement.\n\n---\n\n### 🟢 Trigger\n- **Form submission**\n  - The workflow starts when a contact submits a form requesting an ROI analysis.\n\n---\n\n### ✉️ Initial Action\n- **Send ROI analysis email**\n  - The customer immediately receives a detailed ROI calculation.\n\n---\n\n### 🔀 Branch: Check lifecycle stage\n\nThe workflow adapts its actions based on the contact’s lifecycle stage:\n\n- **Customer** → Notify the Customer Success team in Slack  \n- **Opportunity** → Notify Sales in Slack and create a **“Get in touch”** task  \n- **Lead** → Send a follow-up after 1 day, wait 3 more days, then:\n    - **Positive reply** → Increase lead score by +10  \n    - **No reply** → Add to remarketing audience  \n- **Unknown / Other** → Create a task to manually review the lifecycle stage",
            "size": {
